OL,3,CThree teenagers accused of raping
OL,4,Cyoung girl found not guilty
OL,6,FThree boys accused of raping a teenage
OL,7,Fgirl when they 12, 13, and 14 have
OL,8,Fbeen cleared of all charges.
OL,10,FProsecutors alleged the defendants,
OL,11,Fwho cannot be named due to their ages,
OL,12,Fraped the then-13-year-old girl close
OL,13,Fto the Newbold Tram Stop in Rochdale
OL,14,Fin February 2024.
OL,16,FBut after just under 10 hours of
OL,17,Fdeliberations, the three boys were
OL,18,Fcleared of all charges. They had told
OL,19,Fthe court they had had consensual sex
OL,20,Fwith the girl.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
