CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773940276
OL,3,CThree teenagers accused of raping
OL,4,Cyoung girl found not guilty
OL,6,FIn closing speeches at Manchester
OL,7,FCrown Court, Rachel Shenton, who
OL,8,Frepresented one of the defendants, who
OL,9,Fis now 16-years-old, said consent was
OL,10,F"more nuanced" than "please may I do
OL,11,Fthis to you? Yes".
OL,13,FShe added: "It starts with banter, and
OL,14,Fflirting, with someone walking into
OL,15,Fbushes. They are not middle aged
OL,16,Fpeople, these are adolescents.
OL,18,F"(The alleged victim) herself said 'I
OL,19,Fdidn't say yeah'. Is that enough?"
OL,26,@zD@BpmzD@Upn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
