PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773940276
OL,3,CThree teenagers accused of raping
OL,4,Cyoung girl found not guilty
OL,6,FMs Shenton said the girl had been
OL,7,F"untruthful" and said she flirted on
OL,8,Fthe tram. The evidence, she told
OL,9,Fjurors, showed the girl had been
OL,10,F"inconsistent".
OL,12,F"I asked (the alleged victim) if she
OL,13,Ftold them to 'f*** off'. She did not.
OL,14,FShe went into the bushes. I'm not
OL,15,Fseeking to throw shade at her. She is
OL,16,Fa young girl... immature. Why didn't
OL,17,Fshe shout? Why didn't she scream?"
OL,26,@tD@JpmtD@]pn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
