OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773940276
OL,3,CThree teenagers accused of raping
OL,4,Cyoung girl found not guilty
OL,6,FMs Shenton said the girl had been
OL,7,Fembarrassed about being called a
OL,8,F'sl*g' by two strangers who walked
OL,9,Fpast. She added: "How does she react?
OL,10,F'I was raped'. It is a get out of jail
OL,11,Ffree card. This was not a rape, it was
OL,12,Fa shameful encounter."
OL,14,FPeter Gilmour, representing the now 15-
OL,15,Fyear-old said: "These are children. We
OL,16,Fmust not judge children by the
OL,17,Fstandards of adults."
OL,19,FThe jury was shown footage of the
OL,20,Fincident, which was "circulated among
OL,21,Fthemselves and others".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
