FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773940276
OL,3,CThree teenagers accused of raping
OL,4,Cyoung girl found not guilty
OL,6,FFollowing a two-week trial, the now 16-
OL,7,Fyear-old and the now 15-year-old were
OL,8,Fboth cleared of rape. The boys were
OL,9,Falso cleared of two 'joint enterprise'
OL,10,Fcounts.
OL,12,FJurors were asked to find whether the
OL,13,Fthird boy, now aged 14 and previously
OL,14,Ffound unfit to stand trial, had
OL,15,Fcommitted the acts and whether he had
OL,16,Fencouraged the other boys. Returning
OL,17,Ftheir verdicts, they found he had not
OL,18,Fcommitted the offences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
